videos.headline: Mayock makes pretty catch  for big gain
videos.description: Miami OH Quarterback Billy Bahl connects with Luke Mayock who makes a diving catch down the sideline.

videos.headline: Carrigan takes it 61 yards on the reverse
videos.description: Mike Carrigan runs for 61 yards on a reverse after evading a couple of defenders.

videos.headline: Gardner toe taps for TD
videos.description: Billy Bahl finds James Gardner who displays beautiful footwork for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Golden Flashes get 2nd interception
videos.description: Jamal Parker jumps the screen pass to give the Kent State defense it's second pick of the half.

videos.headline: Bahl throws 2nd TD pass
videos.description: Billy Bahl connects with his tight end Ryan Smith to extend the RedHawks' lead in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Kent State's Bollas finds Rankin for TD
videos.description: George Bollas takes the Golden Flashes 75 yards down the field finishing with a 4-yard touch pass to Justin Rankin for six.

videos.headline: Carrigan goes 84 yards for TD
videos.description: Mike Carrigan records Kent State's longest play of the season sprinting 84 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Gardner makes beautiful diving catch
videos.description: James Gardner puts the RedHawks in field goal range with an impressive diving catch.
